// ║                                                                          ║
// ║   PHASE ROADMAP :                                                        ║
// ║     A.1   Skeleton + Inputs                       ✅ DONE                 ║
// ║     A.2.a Opens + KZ viz + Swings + PO3           ✅ DONE                 ║
// ║     A.2.b PD Arrays (FVG/IFVG/OB/BB) + pastels   ✅ DONE                  ║
// ║     A.2.c Structure (BOS/CHoCH/CISD/MSS)          ✅ DONE ← YOU ARE HERE  ║
// ║     A.2.d-early PDH/PDL/PWH/PWL/PMH/PML           ✅ DONE                 ║
// ║     A.2.d-rest  EQH/EQL + Previous KZ H/L         🔜 NEXT                 ║
// ║     A.2.e P/D/E zones + OTE                                               ║
// ║     A.3  Daily / Weekly bias engine                                      ║
// ║     A.4  Continuation setup logic                                        ║
// ║     A.5  Reversal setup logic                                            ║
// ║     A.6  Filters (KZ, news, SMT, DXY)                                    ║
// ║     A.7  Risk management (sizing, SL/TP, DD)                             ║
// ║     A.8  Performance report                                              ║
// ║     A.9  Walk-forward validation                                         ║
// ║     B.*  Indicator conversion + webhook alerts                           ║
